@config
@CONFIG

Adjust /global/ configuration options for the server.

Syntax: @config <option>         show the current value of this config option
        @config <option> <value> change the value of this config option

Type    Option    values
------- --------- -----------
STRING  color     on, off
STRING  colors    ansi, xterm
INTEGER linelimit 0-?
STRING  msp       on, off

